file_content.text: Oh, you're here, Master Jedi. I just took a weird call from Captain Nelex over at the Republic base.
He said you were coming because some guy was threatening the Junction. Is that right?
Have you seen Cin Tykan today?
I'm looking for a Jedi Master.
Master Tykan? No, I haven't seen him around.
Uh, if this is Jedi business, you should talk to the chief. He knows Tykan better than I do.
Sorry, but I'd rather discuss this with someone senior.
I should speak to your boss.
Keep your voice down! Do you want to start a panic?
So it's true? You'd--you'd better see the chief.
Please, go on in, Master Jedi. And watch your step.
